Source.Name: po4a
Source.Summary: Maintain the translations of your documentation with ease (PO for anything)
Source.Description: The goal of po4a (PO for anything) project is to ease translations (and more interestingly, the maintenance of translations) using gettext tools on areas where they were not expected like documentation.
